headline: Nasdaq Reports September 2025 Volumes and 3Q25 Statistics
summary: NEW YORK, Oct. 07, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Nasdaq (Nasdaq: NDAQ) today reported monthly volumes for September 2025, as well as quarterly volumes, estimated revenue capture, number of listings, and index statistics for the quarter ended September 30, 2025, on its Investor Relations website. A data sheet showing this information can be found at: http://ir.nasdaq.com/financials/volume-statistics. headline: Earnings Preview: What to Expect From Nasdaq’s Report
summary: Nasdaq is expected to post its third-quarter results later this month, and analysts anticipate a low-double-digit earnings growth.
